<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>يَنْصَرِفُ، إِلاَّ أَنَّ الْمَالِكِيَّةَ صَرَّحُوا بِكَرَاهَةِ إِمَامَةِ أَصْحَابِ الأَْعْذَارِ لِلأَْصِحَّاءِ <span class="c2">(١)</span> . وَالتَّفْصِيل فِي مُصْطَلَحِ <span class="c2">(عُذْر)</span> .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>سَلَفٌ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">انْظُرْ:</span> سَلَم، قَرْض<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
